    "en": {
      "title": "Gordon Wilson",
      "content": "👨 Hello! My name's Gordon Wilson. 🏴 I come from Aberdeen in Scotland, but now I live and work in London. 🏠 I have a very small flat near the centre. 🍽️ I'm a waiter and I'm also a drama student. 🇮🇹 I work in an Italian restaurant. 🍝 I eat Italian food and I drink Italian and French wine. 🍺 I don't drink beer. I don't like it. ⚽ And I don't play sports. 🗣️ I speak three languages – English, French, and a little Italian. 🎭 I want to be an actor.",
