      "content": "• Positive: I like tennis.\n• Negative: I don't like football.\n• don't = do not\n• Question: Do you like tennis?\n• Short answer: Yes, I do. / No, I don't.\n• a small flat / an actor / a waiter / an Italian restaurant"
