      "title": "文法のポイント",
      "content": "• 肯定文: I like tennis.（テニスが好きです。）\n• 否定文: I don't like football.（サッカーは好きじゃありません。）\n• don't = do not\n• 疑問文: Do you like tennis?（テニスは好きですか？）\n• 短い答え: Yes, I do. / No, I don't.\n• a small flat（小さなアパート）/ an actor（俳優）/ a waiter（ウェイター）/ an Italian restaurant（イタリア料理店）"
    },
    "fr": {
      "title": "Point de Grammaire",
      "content": "• Positif: I like tennis.\n• Négatif: I don't like football.\n• don't = do not\n• Question: Do you like tennis?\n• Réponse courte: Yes, I do. / No, I don't.\n• a small flat / an actor / a waiter / an Italian restaurant"
    },
    "ko": {
      "title": "문법 포인트",
      "content": "• 긍정문: I like tennis. (나는 테니스를 좋아합니다.)\n• 부정문: I don't like football. (나는 축구를 좋아하지 않습니다.)\n• don't = do not\n• 의문문: Do you like tennis? (테니스를 좋아하세요?)\n• 짧은 답변: Yes, I do. / No, I don't.\n• a small flat (작은 아파트) / an actor (배우) / a waiter (웨이터) / an Italian restaurant (이탈리아 레스토랑)"
    }
  },
